fwix's irssi configuration for GNU/Linux machines

Installation : 

clone from github

    git clone git://github.com/owatte/dotirssi.git ~/.irssi
    mv ~/.irssi/config-distrib ~/.irssi/config
    
replace login and password in ~/.irssi/config    

    vi ~/.irssi/config

final customization : add irssi scripts and create links in the new dir ~/irssi/scripts autorun

    chmod +x ~/.irssi/customize.sh
    ~/.irssi/customize.sh
